window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Profits. Coffee. Extortion. All in a day's work.</b></p> <p>When Ishmael takes the <i>Chernyakova </i>back into Toe-Hold space, he finds a lot more than profit. A quick pass through the Telluride system reveals the answer to one question but leaves him docked without a cargo until the owner of Dark Knight Station makes him an offer he can't refuse.</p>"; 
